<% provide(:title, 'MiniMarketApp') %>
<div class="col-md-offset-4 col-md-4">
    <h1>Mini Market App</h1>
</div>
<div class="col-md-offset-2 col-md-8">
    <p>
    The mini market app was developed to help you
    to manage and create your own brands and products.
    </p>
    <p>
        You can create your brands and then relate it with your products.
    </p>

    <p>
        In a few steps you can start your own business, just click on the 
        images below and then you can become a merchant.
    </p>
</div>
<div class="col-md-offset-2 col-md-8" id="images">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h3>Brands</h3>
        <%= link_to image_tag("brand.png"),brands_path,:class => "imgLikns"%>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h3>Products</h3>
        <%= link_to image_tag("products.png"),products_path,:class => "imgLikns"%>
    </div>
</div>
